recipes.title: Lemon Garlic Shrimp
recipes.description: Quick and flavorful shrimp dish with a zesty lemon garlic sauce Perfect for a weeknight dinner.
ingredients: 1 pound large shrimp, peeled and deveined
preparation: Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.
Add garlic and sauté for 1 minute.
Add shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until pink and cooked through.
Stir in lemon juice and parsley.
Season with salt and pepper to taste.
Serve immediately.

recipes.title: Roasted Vegetable Soups
recipes.description: Hearty and comforting soup made with roasted vegetables and aromatic spices. 123
preparation: Preheat oven to 425°F (220°C).
Toss onion, garlic, carrots, and celery with olive oil and roast for 20-25 minutes, until tender.
In a large pot, combine roasted vegetables, vegetable broth, diced tomatoes, and thyme.
Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 15-20 minutes.
Season with salt and pepper to taste.
Serve hot.
